{"tid":600102,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"毛記1716成超購王 最少超5000倍","createTime":"2018-03-21T04:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T05:22:11.000Z","uid":176676,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60fe5380c98f449d31d5185c5bc89a935a7f564e","tid":600102,"uid":176676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt;   雜誌《100毛》及毛記電視的母公司毛記葵涌(01716已於今早中午截止公開發售,市場消息透露,其錄得最少5000倍超額認購,已遠遠拋離於2014年1月23日掛牌的 Magnum([url=]02080[/url])(現改名為奧克斯國際)超購3558.2倍,成為新的本港史上「超購王」。<br />\n<br />\n由於已超購最少5000倍,遠多於100倍水平,故要啟動回撥機制,毛記公開發售部分佔比由10%,增至50%。<br />\n<br />\n毛記今日定價,料以上限定價,集資1.2億元,本月28日,即下周三掛牌,保薦人為長雄證券。"},{"pid":"a79be73e55c852c466710b8628e48c5094aa631f","tid":600102,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"發行股本咁少<br />\n5000倍其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78d5b3fac49e4384c9ab832246e8e627f99b7b1","tid":600102,"uid":176676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79be73e55c852c466710b8628e48c5094aa631f","tid":600102,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"發行股本咁少<br />\n5000倍其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"我估第一手要實中要1500手了"},{"pid":"4ca3b494f8fde504a2993860a2484c628325946f","tid":600102,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78d5b3fac49e4384c9ab832246e8e627f99b7b1","tid":600102,"uid":176676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79be73e55c852c466710b8628e48c5094aa631f","tid":600102,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"發行股本咁少<br />\n5000倍其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"我估第一手要實中要1500手了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"冇孖到，我想取消個ipo申請得唔得？責住啲錢又唔